"  - 選擇\n"
"    <span class=\"menuchoice\">\n"
"      <span class=\"guimenu\">應用程式</span>&nbsp;▸\n"
"      <span class=\"guisubmenu\">系統工具</span>&nbsp;▸\n"
"      <span class=\"guimenuitem\">超級管理員終端</span></span>.\n"

